<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error Pages - IslamWiki</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: "Inter", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: #2d3748;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2ecc71 0%, #27ae60 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(180deg); }
        }
        
        .header-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: block;
            animation: bounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            40% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
            60% { transform: translateY(-5px); }
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }
        
        .error-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .error-card {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .error-card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2ecc71, #3498db, #e74c3c, #f39c12, #9b59b6);
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .error-card:hover::before {
            transform: scaleX(1);
        }
        
        .error-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-color: #cbd5e0;
        }
        
        .error-card h3 {
            color: #2d3748;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .error-card .error-icon {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
        
        .error-card p {
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .error-card .error-code {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #2ecc71;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .error-card .features {
            list-style: none;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .error-card .features li {
            padding: 5px 0;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 25px;
            color: #4a5568;
        }
        
        .error-card .features li::before {
            content: "✓";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #2ecc71;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .error-card .actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #2ecc71;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #6b7280;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #4b5563;
        }
        
        .btn-danger {
            background: #e74c3c;
        }
        
        .btn-danger:hover {
            background: #c0392b;
        }
        
        .btn-warning {
            background: #f39c12;
        }
        
        .btn-warning:hover {
            background: #e67e22;
        }
        
        .btn-info {
            background: #3498db;
        }
        
        .btn-info:hover {
            background: #2980b9;
        }
        
        .btn-purple {
            background: #9b59b6;
        }
        
        .btn-purple:hover {
            background: #8e44ad;
        }
        
        .info-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #e0f2fe 100%);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9;
        }
        
        .info-section h2 {
            color: #0369a1;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .info-section h2::before {
            content: "ℹ️";
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .info-section p {
            color: #0369a1;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #718096;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            background: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 15px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 40px 20px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .error-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 20px;
            }
            
            .error-card .actions {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .error-card .actions .btn {
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <span class="header-icon">🚀</span>
            <h1>Error Pages Showcase</h1>
            <p>Beautiful, informative error pages designed to help users understand and resolve issues</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="info-section">
                <h2>About Our Error Pages</h2>
                <p>Our error pages are designed with user experience in mind, providing clear information about what went wrong and helpful suggestions for resolving the issue.</p>
                <p>Each error page includes detailed request information, helpful suggestions, and easy navigation options to get users back on track.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="error-grid">
                <div class="error-card">
                    <h3><span class="error-icon">🔍</span>404 Not Found</h3>
                    <span class="error-code">404</span>
                    <p>Page not found error with helpful suggestions and search options.</p>
                    <ul class="features">
                        <li>Request information display</li>
                        <li>Helpful suggestions</li>
                        <li>Search and navigation options</li>
                        <li>Beautiful gradient design</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="actions">
                        <a href="/404" class="btn btn-danger">View 404 Page</a>
                        <a href="/nonexistent-page" class="btn btn-secondary">Trigger 404</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="error-card">
                    <h3><span class="error-icon">🚨</span>500 Server Error</h3>
                    <span class="error-code">500</span>
                    <p>Internal server error with debugging information and recovery options.</p>
                    <ul class="features">
                        <li>Server information display</li>
                        <li>Debug information (when enabled)</li>
                        <li>Recovery suggestions</li>
                        <li>Status checking options</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="actions">
                        <a href="/500" class="btn btn-danger">View 500 Page</a>
                        <a href="/trigger-500" class="btn btn-secondary">Trigger 500</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="error-card">
                    <h3><span class="error-icon">🔒</span>401 Unauthorized</h3>
                    <span class="error-code">401</span>
                    <p>Authentication required error with login options and permission details.</p>
                    <ul class="features">
                        <li>Authentication status</li>
                        <li>Login and registration options</li>
                        <li>Permission requirements</li>
                        <li>Session information</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="actions">
                        <a href="/401" class="btn btn-warning">View 401 Page</a>
                        <a href="/protected-route" class="btn btn-secondary">Trigger 401</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="error-card">
                    <h3><span class="error-icon">🚫</span>403 Forbidden</h3>
                    <span class="error-code">403</span>
                    <p>Access denied error with detailed permission information and alternatives.</p>
                    <ul class="features">
                        <li>Access control details</li>
                        <li>Permission requirements</li>
                        <li>Alternative suggestions</li>
                        <li>Support contact options</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="actions">
                        <a href="/403" class="btn btn-warning">View 403 Page</a>
                        <a href="/admin-only" class="btn btn-secondary">Trigger 403</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="error-card">
                    <h3><span class="error-icon">⏰</span>429 Too Many Requests</h3>
                    <span class="error-code">429</span>
                    <p>Rate limiting error with countdown timer and retry options.</p>
                    <ul class="features">
                        <li>Rate limit information</li>
                        <li>Countdown timer</li>
                        <li>Retry suggestions</li>
                        <li>Limit policy details</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="actions">
                        <a href="/429" class="btn btn-info">View 429 Page</a>
                        <a href="/rate-limited" class="btn btn-secondary">Trigger 429</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="error-card">
                    <h3><span class="error-icon">🔧</span>503 Service Unavailable</h3>
                    <span class="error-code">503</span>
                    <p>Maintenance mode error with status updates and estimated completion time.</p>
                    <ul class="features">
                        <li>Maintenance status</li>
                        <li>Estimated completion time</li>
                        <li>Alternative resources</li>
                        <li>Status page links</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="actions">
                        <a href="/503" class="btn btn-purple">View 503 Page</a>
                        <a href="/maintenance" class="btn btn-secondary">Trigger 503</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="error-card">
                    <h3><span class="error-icon">📝</span>422 Unprocessable Entity</h3>
                    <span class="error-code">422</span>
                    <p>Validation error with detailed field information and correction suggestions.</p>
                    <ul class="features">
                        <li>Validation error details</li>
                        <li>Field-specific information</li>
                        <li>Correction suggestions</li>
                        <li>Form data display</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="actions">
                        <a href="/422" class="btn btn-info">View 422 Page</a>
                        <a href="/invalid-form" class="btn btn-secondary">Trigger 422</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-section">
                <h2>Features & Benefits</h2>
                <p><strong>User Experience:</strong> Clear error messages, helpful suggestions, and easy navigation options.</p>
                <p><strong>Developer Friendly:</strong> Detailed debug information when enabled, request details, and server context.</p>
                <p><strong>Responsive Design:</strong> Mobile-friendly layouts that work on all devices and screen sizes.</p>
                <p><strong>Accessibility:</strong> High contrast colors, clear typography, and semantic HTML structure.</p>
                <p><strong>Customization:</strong> Easy to modify colors, icons, and content for different error types.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>IslamWiki - Islamic Knowledge Platform</p>
            <p>Beautiful error pages designed to help users navigate and resolve issues effectively.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 